'''CGI集團'''（'''CGI Group Inc.'''） 是一家總部位於[[加拿大|加拿大]][[蒙特利爾|蒙特利爾]]的[[跨國公司|跨國公司]]，業務涉及IT諮詢和外包服務及其相關產業。2012年以27億加元的價格收購英國IT服務公司[[Logica|Logica]]，因此成為世界第五大獨立IT服務供應商。<ref>{{cite web|title=CGI completes Logica acquisition and announces new operations leadership team|url=http://www.cgi.com/en/CGI-completes-Logica-acquisition-new-leadership-team|work=CGI.com|accessdate=19 November 2013|archive-date=2013-12-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131203140700/http://www.cgi.com/en/CGI-completes-Logica-acquisition-new-leadership-team|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==命名==
[[File:E-Commerce_Place.jpg|thumb]]
CGI來自於[[法語|法語]]“Conseillers en Gestion et Informatique”，意即“信息系統和管理諮詢”，不過官方的英語名稱卻是“Consultants to Government and Industry”（給政府與產業提供諮詢）。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.cgi.com/en/careers/cgi-integration |title=Integrating into CGI |access-date=2013-12-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110721035405/http://www.cgi.com/en/careers/cgi-integration |archive-date=2011-07-21 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

==歷史==
1976年6月，CGI集團由Serge Godin成立於[[希庫蒂米|希庫蒂米]]，<ref>{{cite web|title=Our History|url=http://www.cgi.com/files/pdf/cgi_history.pdf|publisher=CGI Group|accessdate=26 August 2012|archive-date=2013-10-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131029195311/http://www.cgi.com/files/pdf/cgi_history.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref> 2004年買下大部份[[美國系統管理公司|美國系統管理公司]]，獲得其所有商業業務和與國防無關的政府業務。它也是[[美國|美國]]2006年減稅與健康法案（Tax Relief and Health Care Act of 2006）中規定的四家主要恢復審計承包商（Recovery Audit Contractor）之一。<ref>{{cite web |title=Overview: Recovery Audit Contractor |url=http://www.cms.gov/RAC/ |publisher=[[Centers_for_Medicare_and_Medicaid_Services|Centers for Medicare and Medicaid Services]] |accessdate=26 February 2011 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110129045740/http://www.cms.gov/RAC/ |archivedate=2011-01-29 }}</ref> 2009年其子公司[[CGI聯邦|CGI聯邦]]得到價值14億美元的美國聯邦合同，2012-13財年其收入有很大一部份都是來自於[[美國聯邦政府|美國聯邦政府]]。<ref>{{citation |publisher=Reuters |url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2013/11/19/us-usa-healthcare-contracting-insight-idUSBRE9AI05S20131119 |title=Insight: Health site woes show Washington misses out on cutting edge technology |author=Andy Sullivan |date=November 19, 2013 |accessdate=2013-12-01 |archive-date=2013-12-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131203031747/http://www.reuters.com/article/2013/11/19/us-usa-healthcare-contracting-insight-idUSBRE9AI05S20131119 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2010年5月宣佈收購Stanley, Inc.，該公司當時的[[企業價值|企業價值]]為10.7億美元。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.newstatesman.com/technology/2010/05/cgi-stanley-cash-services |title=CGI Group to acquire Stanley for $1.07bn |accessdate=2013-12-01 |archive-date=2013-10-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131029201313/http://www.newstatesman.com/technology/2010/05/cgi-stanley-cash-services |dead-url=no }}</ref> 同年8月收購完成。<ref>{{cite web|title=CGI’s Acquisition of Stanley Finalized|url=http://www.govconwire.com/2010/08/breaking-cgis-acquisition-of-stanley-finalized/|publisher=GovConWire|accessdate=24 August 2012|archive-date=2013-10-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131029192819/http://www.govconwire.com/2010/08/breaking-cgis-acquisition-of-stanley-finalized/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 2012年5月以27億加元的價格收購英國IT服務公司[[Logica|Logica]]，<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/finance/newsbysector/mediatechnologyandtelecoms/electronics/9302110/Logica-agrees-1.7bn-takeover-by-Canadas-CGI.html|title=Logica agrees £1.7bn takeover by Canada's CGI|accessdate=31 May 2012|publisher=The Telegraph|date=31 May 2012|archive-date=2013-12-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131222013243/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/finance/newsbysector/mediatechnologyandtelecoms/electronics/9302110/Logica-agrees-1.7bn-takeover-by-Canadas-CGI.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/business-18279030|title=Logica agrees to be bought by Canadian rival CGI|accessdate=31 May 2012|publisher=BBC News|date=31 May 2012|archive-date=2012-08-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120815085625/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/business-18279030|dead-url=no}}</ref> 同年8月20日收購完成。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.businessweek.com/ap/2012-08-20/cgi-group-closes-2-dot-67b-deal-for-uk-based-logica|title=CGI Group closes $2.67B deal for UK-based Logica|accessdate=20 August 2012|publisher=Bloomberg Businessweek|date=20 August 2012|archive-date=2013-05-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130506090416/http://www.businessweek.com/ap/2012-08-20/cgi-group-closes-2-dot-67b-deal-for-uk-based-logica|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2011年CGI开始参与美国联邦政府医疗网站{{link-en|HealthCare.gov|HealthCare.gov}}的建设。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.npr.org/blogs/alltechconsidered/2013/10/23/240242572/its-easy-to-blame-the-canadians-for-healthcare-gov-glitches |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2014-08-10 |archive-date=2014-08-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140825114407/http://www.npr.org/blogs/alltechconsidered/2013/10/23/240242572/its-easy-to-blame-the-canadians-for-healthcare-gov-glitches |dead-url=no }}</ref>但是该网站在2013年上线后遇到了很严重的技术问题。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/blogs/wonkblog/wp/2013/10/16/meet-cgi-federal-the-company-behind-the-botched-launch-of-healthcare-gov/ |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2014-08-10 |archive-date=2014-08-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140826150329/http://www.washingtonpost.com/blogs/wonkblog/wp/2013/10/16/meet-cgi-federal-the-company-behind-the-botched-launch-of-healthcare-gov/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2021年10月4日，CGI (GIB) 表示，CGI Federal Inc. 收购了 Array Holding Company，这是一家为美国国防部和其他政府组织优化任务性能的数字服务提供商。两家公司于 7 月 16 日签署了最终协议，交易于 10 月 1 日完成。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.mg21.com/gib.html|title=加拿大政府机构及军方资讯技术服务提供商：CGI Inc.(GIB)|publisher=美股之家|date=2021-10-05|access-date=2021-10-08|archive-date=2021-10-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211008202811/https://www.mg21.com/gib.html/}}</ref>

